  "body": "<p>The other day I was trying to come up with a mini manifesto for the moment. I wrote the word simplify. And because that just wasn't enough, I just kept writing.</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1598682236606-GWZWFA0MROPGND6MYUIX/5a-20140805-231954-83994317.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>The brush says Royal 2 on it, but can't remember where it's from, sorry! I used <a href=\"http://www.michaels.com/artists-loft-fundamentals-watercolor-pan-set/10122060.html#q=watercolor&amp;start=2\">this watercolor set from Michaels</a>, but found some alternative options - <a href=\"http://www.shareasale.com/r.cfm?u=530666&amp;b=33086&amp;m=7429&amp;afftrack=watercolor&amp;urllink=store%2Escrapbook%2Ecom%2Fac%2D366901%2Ehtml\">Colortopia Watercolor Set</a> | <a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/gp/product/B00114RIIQ/ref=as_li_tl?ie=UTF8&amp;camp=1789&amp;creative=390957&amp;creativeASIN=B00114RIIQ&amp;linkCode=as2&amp;tag=wwwamytangeri-20&amp;linkId=SEL4W2XO57Q&lt;a%20href=\">this one</a> | <a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/gp/product/B0019IKY58/ref=as_li_tl?ie=UTF8&amp;camp=1789&amp;creative=390957&amp;creativeASIN=B0019IKY58&amp;linkCode=as2&amp;tag=wwwamytangeri-20&amp;linkId=Y4TM3YCBZ74FFNPO\">and this one</a></p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>"
